The,Backblaze,B,Cloud,Storage,API,is,a,cloud,service,tool,for,storing,files,in,the,cloud,With,the,B,Cloud,Storage,API,users,can,manage,the,configuration,of,their,accounts,create,and,manage,the,buckets,that,hold,files,and,upload,download,and,delete,files,Backblaze,provides,user,friendly,unlimited,and,efficient,storage,and,back,up,options,and,services